component.script:
sub Init() m.itemText = m.top.findNode("itemText") m.itemText.text = "Loading..." end sub
function itemContentChanged() as void ' re-declare this because init doesnt re-run ' when we come back from elsewhere m.itemText = m.top.findNode("itemText")
itemData = m.top.itemContent m.itemText.text = itemData.labelText end function
